//Trauma


Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 02 - Anamnesis of Knee MRI


When I select 'Trauma' checkbox
Then 'Twisted' radio button is enabled
And 'Fall' radio button is enabled
And 'Month' dropdown menu of Date of trauma is enabled
And 'Year' dropdown menu of Date of trauma is enabled

When I select 'Twisted' radio button
Then 'Low velocity' radio button is enabled
And 'High velocity' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Patella luxation' checkbox
Then 'Month' dropdown menu of Date of Luxation is enabled
And 'Year' dropdown menu of Date of Luxation is enabled


When I select 'Fracture' checkbox
Then 'Femur' checkbox is enabled
And 'Tibia' checkbox is enabled
And 'Fibula' checkbox is enabled
And 'Patella' checkbox is enabled
